WEBVTT

01:34.800 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:43.240 --> 01:44.480
ONE DAY

01:47.360 --> 01:48.840
- Excuse me!
- Watch out!

01:48.920 --> 01:50.840
- Sorry! Be careful!
- Thank you!

01:50.920 --> 01:52.080
- Watch out!
- Sorry!

01:52.720 --> 01:53.560
WUSHI NO.1 SENIOR HIGH SCHOOL

01:55.280 --> 01:56.320
- I'm leaving, Dad.
- Okay.

01:57.120 --> 01:58.600
If you don't understand
something, just ask!

01:58.680 --> 01:59.520
Got it!

02:04.800 --> 02:06.240
That was the first time I saw her.

02:11.840 --> 02:14.160
How do I get her to notice me?

02:16.160 --> 02:17.880
Lend me your ball for a sec.
I'll give it right back.

02:17.960 --> 02:20.560
- I didn't even agree yet!
- I'll buy you a drink!

02:42.000 --> 02:44.520
That was the first time I saw him.

02:47.800 --> 02:49.960
Senior, can you tell me
how to get to Class 17?

02:50.800 --> 02:51.720
Sorry, I'm a freshman.

02:53.320 --> 02:54.960
Go down the stairs,
turn left, and enter the building.

02:58.440 --> 03:01.000
- Then?
- Then…

03:01.680 --> 03:03.640
Then look at the room numbers yourself.

03:03.720 --> 03:06.000
What, you want me
to read them all out for you,

03:08.160 --> 03:09.480
Junior?

03:10.720 --> 03:11.560
Thanks, Senior.

03:17.400 --> 03:18.600
Hey, my basketball!

03:53.320 --> 03:54.560
So, this is your house?

04:05.880 --> 04:07.920
I've never seen you put
so much effort into makeup.

04:08.000 --> 04:08.840
What's the occasion?

04:09.360 --> 04:10.280
Uh…

04:10.360 --> 04:11.800
I'm just a little nervous.

04:15.800 --> 04:18.160
You already look amazing. Really.

04:22.640 --> 04:24.960
You even prepared lines
to meet my parents?

04:25.480 --> 04:27.520
I just don't want to say something wrong.

04:30.120 --> 04:33.120
Alright, relax.
You've got me to distract them.

04:34.800 --> 04:35.640
Let me see what you wrote.

04:36.840 --> 04:38.600
Not just lines, there's even an act.

04:38.680 --> 04:40.600
- What act?
- Look.

04:41.240 --> 04:42.280
Keep smiling.

04:43.840 --> 04:45.880
No fake smiles.

04:45.960 --> 04:47.400
No big grins either.

04:47.480 --> 04:48.840
Show me.

04:55.600 --> 04:57.360
- Yifan! Please come in.
- Zhi.

04:58.120 --> 04:59.800
- Happy New Year!
- Happy New Year!

05:00.680 --> 05:03.360
- This is a New Year's gift for you.
- Thank you!

05:03.960 --> 05:05.160
Mom!

05:05.680 --> 05:07.280
Is Yifan here?

05:07.800 --> 05:08.880
Auntie, Happy New Year!

05:08.960 --> 05:10.200
Happy New Year!

05:10.280 --> 05:12.560
Mom, Yifan brought gifts for you.

05:12.640 --> 05:15.520
Next time, just come over.
No need to bring anything.

05:15.600 --> 05:17.040
Come sit. Dinner's almost ready.

05:17.120 --> 05:19.120
- Let me help.
- No need. It'll be done in a bit.

05:19.200 --> 05:20.560
Come, have a seat.

05:22.040 --> 05:22.920
Oh, Yifan's here!

05:23.000 --> 05:25.080
- Welcome!
- Uncle, Happy New Year!

05:25.160 --> 05:27.600
Happy New Year! You can watch TV with Zhi.

05:27.680 --> 05:28.560
Alright.

05:31.600 --> 05:32.840
Where are you going?

05:32.920 --> 05:33.880
Watching TV.

05:33.960 --> 05:35.760
Go watch at your own house.

05:35.840 --> 05:37.640
- Mom, he's kicking me out!
- You're really going to tattle?

05:37.720 --> 05:40.480
Ping, our son wants to watch TV.
Shouldn't we say something?

05:41.240 --> 05:43.320
Watch TV? You're a grown man.

05:43.400 --> 05:45.640
Go help out in the kitchen!
Take your time.

05:45.720 --> 05:47.160
You guys chat.

05:47.240 --> 05:48.120
I'll go make tea.

05:48.200 --> 05:50.560
Did your brother upset your parents?

05:50.640 --> 05:51.480
Before you arrived,

05:51.560 --> 05:54.240
they'd been nagging him
for almost four hours.

05:54.320 --> 05:56.280
They started as soon
as they began cooking,

05:56.360 --> 05:59.280
complaining that he never comes home,
never texts, never calls,

05:59.360 --> 06:01.040
and never gives them
an update on his life.

06:01.120 --> 06:03.800
They practically had to beg
just to get him back for a meal.

06:03.880 --> 06:07.600
If it weren't for bringing you home,
he probably wouldn't even be back.

06:08.640 --> 06:10.200
He's too caught up in his romance.

06:10.280 --> 06:11.560
My brother must really like you.

06:11.640 --> 06:14.280
Otherwise, he wouldn't
put up with their nagging.

06:14.920 --> 06:17.040
Come on. Have some tea.

06:18.120 --> 06:18.960
Thank you, Uncle.

06:19.040 --> 06:20.320
You're so polite!
Just make yourself at home.

06:22.040 --> 06:23.040
Are you sick?

06:23.120 --> 06:24.840
Let me see. Do you have a fever?

06:24.920 --> 06:26.200
- Oh, you got a fever?
- What's wrong?

06:26.280 --> 06:27.160
Just feeling a little cold inside.

06:27.240 --> 06:29.000
- You don't have a fever?
- This kid…

06:29.080 --> 06:31.400
But you really don't look well.

06:31.480 --> 06:32.760
Have you been staying up late again?

06:34.040 --> 06:35.120
Skipping meals too?

06:35.640 --> 06:38.160
I tried to help you rebuild your health,
but you wouldn't come home.

06:38.240 --> 06:39.160
I'm this young,

06:39.240 --> 06:40.280
- and I already need to rebuild my health?
- Sorry.

06:40.360 --> 06:42.600
Hey, if you wait until my age,
it'll be too late!

06:42.680 --> 06:43.520
- You know that?
- Alright, enough.

06:43.600 --> 06:44.960
Look how upset you're making your mom.

06:45.040 --> 06:46.520
Look at you, lost weight again.

06:47.880 --> 06:48.840
Such a loving family!

06:49.640 --> 06:51.080
- Did you lose weight?
- No.

06:51.160 --> 06:52.480
Look at you, so stubborn.

06:52.560 --> 06:53.880
If he hadn't met me,

06:55.080 --> 06:57.520
Sang Yan could have lived a peaceful life.

06:58.640 --> 06:59.760
That wouldn't have been good.

07:03.480 --> 07:04.800
Back then,

07:04.880 --> 07:06.760
my brother suddenly
started studying like crazy.

07:06.840 --> 07:09.680
A failing student like him
finally got into Nanwu University.

07:09.760 --> 07:11.040
You encouraged him, didn't you?

07:19.680 --> 07:22.400
We had agreed
to go to the same university.

07:22.480 --> 07:24.720
But in the end, you chose Yihe University.

07:25.520 --> 07:26.960
Was it because of your grades?

07:28.360 --> 07:30.480
No, I deliberately didn't apply
to Nanwu University.

07:31.200 --> 07:32.440
So, you fell for someone else?

07:34.800 --> 07:37.920
I never liked anyone else.
Not in the past. Not in the future.

07:42.320 --> 07:44.120
He was really devastated.

07:45.000 --> 07:49.080
That was the first time
I thought he was like a lump of clay,

07:50.360 --> 07:51.960
with no charm whatsoever.

07:53.880 --> 07:56.760
That whole summer,
he locked himself in his room.

07:57.280 --> 07:59.440
He had no motivation to do anything.

08:02.800 --> 08:03.720
Sang Yan, drink some porridge.

08:10.760 --> 08:12.000
Sang Yan, take your medicine.

08:25.120 --> 08:26.160
Sang Yan, have a jelly.

08:26.240 --> 08:28.000
Get some sugar in you.

08:37.120 --> 08:38.760
Actually, this was a good thing.

08:40.559 --> 08:42.919
- Why?
- He's always been smart,

08:43.919 --> 08:45.800
good at everything since childhood,

08:45.880 --> 08:47.880
always so arrogant, full of himself.

08:47.960 --> 08:49.880
Even with family, he kept his distance.

08:49.960 --> 08:54.120
Then he decided school was useless
and only did what he liked.

08:55.080 --> 08:58.000
Everyone indulged him,
but the more they spoiled him,

08:58.720 --> 08:59.800
the harder he was to deal with.

09:01.080 --> 09:02.160
I couldn't get close to him either.

09:03.120 --> 09:04.080
Until later,

09:06.960 --> 09:10.760
when he experienced
a failure as big as losing you.

09:11.760 --> 09:12.840
That's when he finally understood

09:12.920 --> 09:15.760
the world doesn't revolve around him.

09:31.760 --> 09:33.640
Sang Yan, what's wrong with you?

09:42.600 --> 09:46.000
The family has been so happy
that you got into Nanwu University.

09:46.080 --> 09:48.080
They even told me to learn from you.

09:50.520 --> 09:53.360
What's there to learn from me?
I'm terrible.

09:53.440 --> 09:54.600
Who said you're terrible?

09:54.680 --> 09:56.960
Tell me. I want to be friends with him!

10:01.080 --> 10:02.560
Sang Yan, you're heartbroken, aren't you?

10:05.720 --> 10:07.680
What does a little kid like you know?

10:07.760 --> 10:08.960
Why wouldn't I know?

10:09.040 --> 10:11.560
In fairy tales, when the prince
can't find the princess,

10:11.640 --> 10:12.680
he looks just like you!

10:19.280 --> 10:20.120
And then?

10:21.480 --> 10:24.360
Then the prince endured countless trials,

10:24.440 --> 10:26.040
mastered all kinds of skills,

10:26.120 --> 10:27.960
and crossed snowy mountains, deserts,

10:28.040 --> 10:29.600
and forests full of monsters.

10:30.320 --> 10:31.920
In the end,

10:32.920 --> 10:35.280
he saved the princess,
and they lived happily ever after.

10:47.160 --> 10:49.840
Kid, you sure know a lot.

10:50.520 --> 10:53.920
I'm not a kid anymore. You don't
even know how good cartoons are!

10:54.880 --> 10:56.720
Here, have a jelly. Get some sugar in you.

11:12.720 --> 11:14.960
- What food do we have?
- Weren't you skipping dinner?

11:15.040 --> 11:18.000
Mom! Put away
the chicken drumsticks and steak!

11:18.600 --> 11:19.440
Here.

11:19.520 --> 11:21.240
That's when I realized

11:21.760 --> 11:24.120
he was someone I could be close to.

11:25.240 --> 11:27.280
He was no longer
just that serious older brother,

11:28.840 --> 11:30.720
but someone I could actually connect with.

11:32.440 --> 11:33.800
We changed each other

11:34.880 --> 11:36.480
and became better versions of ourselves.

11:37.360 --> 11:39.920
Come on. Drink up.

11:40.560 --> 11:41.640
- Here.
- Yifan,

11:41.720 --> 11:43.040
it's all home-cooked food today.

11:43.120 --> 11:44.600
We don't see you as an outsider.

11:44.680 --> 11:46.120
Thank you, Uncle, Auntie.

11:46.200 --> 11:47.520
No need to be polite.

11:47.600 --> 11:49.520
- Here. Try my cooking.
- No need to be so formal.

11:50.040 --> 11:50.880
Eat more.

11:50.960 --> 11:52.720
- This is her specialty dish.
- Yes.

12:02.360 --> 12:04.440
Is my makeup smudged?

12:07.160 --> 12:08.560
No.

12:08.640 --> 12:09.600
Yifan,

12:10.600 --> 12:11.920
you're really beautiful!

12:13.480 --> 12:17.000
Ping, you're staring too much.
You're making her embarrassed.

12:17.520 --> 12:19.920
But Yifan, ever since
we met you in high school,

12:20.000 --> 12:22.200
she has been saying the same thing.

12:22.800 --> 12:24.160
- Right.
- She even said,

12:24.240 --> 12:26.760
"Look at our Yan.
How is he even worthy of a girl like her?"

12:26.840 --> 12:28.800
- Right?
- Exactly. She's stunning.

12:31.880 --> 12:32.920
What are you laughing at?

12:34.000 --> 12:35.680
How do you talk to your sister like that?

12:35.760 --> 12:36.880
This kid…

12:37.440 --> 12:39.720
- Come on, eat. Eat up.
- Dig in.

12:39.800 --> 12:41.720
Let me try this dumpling filling.

12:41.800 --> 12:44.040
Honestly, back in high school,
we weren't dating.

12:45.080 --> 12:46.560
We only…

12:46.640 --> 12:49.600
When I was on a business trip in Beiyu,
he came to find me.

12:49.680 --> 12:50.720
That's when we actually got together.

12:55.320 --> 12:57.160
Either way, he liked you from the start.

12:57.240 --> 12:59.320
That never changed. He's so stubborn.

13:00.880 --> 13:03.480
- He really thought we didn't know?
- It's true.

13:03.560 --> 13:06.560
He's been out of college for years,
and still didn't date anyone.

13:07.440 --> 13:08.960
We were so worried.

13:09.040 --> 13:11.080
We even thought
that conversation back then

13:11.160 --> 13:12.640
scared him off.

13:12.720 --> 13:15.120
Yeah. We even tried
setting him up on blind dates.

13:15.200 --> 13:16.720
You even introduced me to a foreigner.

13:22.800 --> 13:26.880
FORTUNE

13:26.960 --> 13:28.600
Now comes the important part!

13:28.680 --> 13:29.600
Here.

13:29.680 --> 13:31.280
- Thank you, Mom.
- You're welcome.

13:31.360 --> 13:33.480
- Here.
- Thank you.

13:34.120 --> 13:34.960
Here.

13:36.320 --> 13:38.520
- I get one too?
- Of course.

13:38.600 --> 13:40.720
From now on, you're family.

13:41.400 --> 13:42.560
Take it.

13:43.400 --> 13:44.400
Take it.

13:44.920 --> 13:46.240
Take it.

13:48.960 --> 13:50.120
Thank you, Auntie.

13:50.640 --> 13:52.760
No need to be so polite. Come on. Eat up.

13:52.840 --> 13:54.640
- Come on.
- Don't drink too much.

13:54.720 --> 13:56.000
- Take it easy on the drinks.
- Alright.

13:56.080 --> 13:57.120
Let Yifan eat more.

13:57.200 --> 13:58.400
Here, some shrimp.

13:59.520 --> 14:02.080
Finally, I feel like I have a family.

14:02.920 --> 14:04.800
Come on. Eat up.

14:13.360 --> 14:15.480
Being part of their family,

14:18.800 --> 14:21.800
feeling their love,
completely wrapped in warmth…

14:22.640 --> 14:23.760
It's such a good feeling.

14:24.440 --> 14:27.160
Yifan, this is my room.

14:27.240 --> 14:28.280
Have a seat.

14:29.000 --> 14:32.000
Stay with me tonight.
I'll tell you my secret.

14:35.120 --> 14:36.760
- Let me take this call first.
- Okay.

14:39.480 --> 14:40.680
Hello? Jiaxu?

14:40.760 --> 14:41.960
Zhi, Happy New Year!

14:42.040 --> 14:43.160
Happy New Year!

14:44.480 --> 14:48.360
We had dumplings. And… my mom made ribs.

14:50.560 --> 14:51.600
Yeah, I read it.

14:53.640 --> 14:54.800
What?

14:57.600 --> 14:58.800
No, I didn't.

15:00.600 --> 15:02.040
I didn't get to that part.

15:15.920 --> 15:17.000
The door wasn't locked.

15:36.760 --> 15:37.960
We're home!

15:39.640 --> 15:40.640
You can't sleep?

15:42.000 --> 15:42.960
I'll sleep later.

15:43.840 --> 15:46.640
- Want to sleep with me?
- No.

15:47.360 --> 15:48.360
Then go.

15:49.360 --> 15:50.600
The door's still open.

15:52.200 --> 15:53.200
Sit down.

16:11.240 --> 16:12.600
Why are you still awake?

16:13.680 --> 16:14.720
Waiting for someone.

16:21.360 --> 16:23.040
Tomorrow, are you staying here?

16:31.560 --> 16:32.920
I really like your home.

16:34.560 --> 16:36.000
What's so great about my place?

16:38.960 --> 16:42.280
It's just such a happy and warm family.

16:43.200 --> 16:44.800
Only a home like this
could raise someone like you.

16:48.000 --> 16:48.960
Someone like me?

16:54.240 --> 16:55.320
What kind of person am I?

16:57.400 --> 16:58.440
Proud.

17:01.000 --> 17:03.240
Confident. Passionate.

17:04.680 --> 17:05.560
Like the sun.

17:11.760 --> 17:12.680
Sang Yan,

17:13.960 --> 17:16.720
your sister's nickname is Zhī.
Do you have one?

17:17.440 --> 17:19.880
Should it be a first-tone sound too?

17:21.640 --> 17:24.920
- Yān?
- Wen Yifan, are you sleepwalking?

17:25.000 --> 17:26.160
What nonsense are you talking about?

17:26.240 --> 17:28.040
Or should it be a second-tone? Yán?

17:29.160 --> 17:31.080
Enough. I don't have one.

17:34.800 --> 17:35.800
Then…

17:39.320 --> 17:40.240
I'll just call you Yán.

17:47.680 --> 17:48.920
I'm going to bed.

17:51.080 --> 17:52.440
Wait.

17:53.920 --> 17:54.760
What did you just call me?

17:55.440 --> 17:56.440
Yán.

17:57.160 --> 17:58.520
Then, from now on,

17:59.720 --> 18:00.680
always call me that.

18:17.200 --> 18:18.520
Alright, time to sleep.

18:22.160 --> 18:23.160
Good night.

18:24.080 --> 18:25.000
Good night.

18:36.560 --> 18:39.480
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

18:41.840 --> 18:43.480
How's the packing going, my fairy?

18:44.720 --> 18:46.360
- Are you tired?
- No, I'm good.

18:47.280 --> 18:48.720
Do you need help with anything else?

18:51.120 --> 18:53.120
- Help me pack my books.
- Okay.

18:53.640 --> 18:55.920
The moving company is almost here.
We need to hurry.

19:02.080 --> 19:03.520
MU CHENGYUN

19:06.840 --> 19:08.720
MU CHENGYUN

19:12.280 --> 19:14.840
Mu Chengyun.

19:15.360 --> 19:18.080
Wen Shuangjiang, you've got some nerve.

19:22.520 --> 19:23.560
What?

19:24.160 --> 19:26.640
Why are you still keeping a signature

19:26.720 --> 19:28.960
from a colleague who had a crush on you?

19:29.040 --> 19:30.960
What nonsense. It's been there so long.
I forgot about it.

19:32.280 --> 19:33.760
Who does he think he is?
Why did he leave you a signature?

19:33.840 --> 19:35.120
Does he owe you money?

19:36.600 --> 19:38.960
He was the creepy kid
in that movie Waking up to Ghosts.

19:39.040 --> 19:41.600
Don't you remember?
We watched it together so many times.

19:43.560 --> 19:45.760
I remember. That kid…

19:46.280 --> 19:47.400
He was a pretty good actor.

19:48.440 --> 19:50.000
Then, why do I recall
someone covering his eyes

19:50.080 --> 19:51.640
the whole time while watching?

19:53.560 --> 19:56.880
No way. You must be mistaken.
I watched it seriously.

19:56.960 --> 19:58.680
That kid's face was completely pale.

19:59.440 --> 20:01.280
Not bad, though. Keep it.

20:03.400 --> 20:06.240
Do you have any empty boxes left?
I can't fit all my stuff.

20:06.760 --> 20:08.600
I think there's
an unpacked box in my room.

20:08.680 --> 20:10.560
- Check it out.
- Okay.

20:21.920 --> 20:23.840
I'll take out the records!

20:24.880 --> 20:25.880
Alright.

20:33.960 --> 20:35.800
Do you still need this tin box?

21:02.360 --> 21:04.040
HAPPY GRADUATION

21:20.320 --> 21:23.240
NANWU TO YIHE

21:24.080 --> 21:27.800
NANWU TO YIHE

21:30.520 --> 21:33.520
NAME: SANG YAN, DESTINATION: YIHE

21:39.560 --> 21:42.720
NAME: SANG YAN, DESTINATION: YIHE

21:47.280 --> 21:49.960
Last city you flew to?

21:50.040 --> 21:52.120
What kind of dumb question is that?
Who cares?

21:52.200 --> 21:53.160
Yihe.

21:58.680 --> 22:00.360
NAME: SANG YAN, DESTINATION: YIHE

22:07.360 --> 22:10.720
INTERN REPORTER: WEN YIFAN

22:11.720 --> 22:14.640
This was my first published article
as an intern.

22:15.960 --> 22:19.520
YIHE DAILY, REPORTER: WEN YIFAN

22:20.360 --> 22:22.800
And this is the one I wrote
the day I became a full-time reporter.

22:29.840 --> 22:31.480
How's it going? Can it all fit?

22:33.320 --> 22:35.480
I made you a cup of brown sugar water.

22:35.560 --> 22:36.560
Drink it while it's hot.

22:54.520 --> 22:55.800
All these years,

22:58.360 --> 23:00.040
you've gone to Yihe so many times.

23:00.120 --> 23:01.720
Didn't I

23:02.960 --> 23:04.240
tell you before?

23:06.000 --> 23:07.000
No matter what happens,

23:09.240 --> 23:10.440
I'll always be here for you.

23:16.680 --> 23:17.840
What's wrong?

23:28.760 --> 23:30.160
Wen Shuangjiang,

23:31.800 --> 23:32.920
no crying.

23:35.000 --> 23:36.800
Before you were with me,

23:37.320 --> 23:39.000
you never cried, no matter what happened.

23:40.120 --> 23:43.120
But after we got together,
do you know how many times you've cried?

23:49.880 --> 23:51.040
Actually,

23:53.920 --> 23:55.800
I saw you at my graduation.

23:57.040 --> 23:58.960
But I thought I was mistaken.

24:15.280 --> 24:18.880
Mistaking me for someone else
might have been a good thing.

24:20.960 --> 24:24.320
If you had recognized me,
wouldn't I have lost all my pride?

24:26.640 --> 24:28.720
I even secretly ran off to find you.

24:32.720 --> 24:35.200
Back then, I should have
gone straight to you.

24:39.000 --> 24:42.320
Why did I ever treat you so badly?

24:52.800 --> 24:53.880
What's up?

24:54.920 --> 24:56.640
Didn't we already make up?

25:03.360 --> 25:05.080
Or…

25:05.720 --> 25:07.880
is there something else
you feel guilty about?

25:15.440 --> 25:16.360
I…

25:17.400 --> 25:18.280
I took advantage of you once.

25:18.360 --> 25:20.320
You took advantage of me?

25:21.680 --> 25:23.080
Isn't that something you do every day?

25:24.600 --> 25:26.040
Before we were together…

25:29.800 --> 25:31.400
Before we were together?

25:32.760 --> 25:35.080
I once pretended
to sleepwalk and hugged you.

25:37.600 --> 25:39.160
Wen Shuangjiang,

25:39.920 --> 25:41.360
you actually did that?

25:42.600 --> 25:45.000
Consider it exercising
my rights in advance.

25:48.400 --> 25:50.760
Back then, didn't you act all proper?

25:51.400 --> 25:53.080
Turns out you had other thoughts.

26:01.160 --> 26:02.080
Stop crying.

26:10.200 --> 26:11.600
Weren't you packing?

26:12.160 --> 26:13.480
All done?

26:21.680 --> 26:22.720
Yan,

26:27.240 --> 26:29.080
I want to live six years longer than you.

26:32.840 --> 26:33.800
Why?

26:36.600 --> 26:38.120
That way, I can love you
for six more years

26:43.480 --> 26:44.960
to make up

26:45.880 --> 26:48.440
for the days I left you behind.

26:52.200 --> 26:53.560
Then we'll be even.

27:02.240 --> 27:06.040
I think I get what you're saying.

27:08.560 --> 27:09.520
But…

27:09.600 --> 27:11.720
I still want to live
a few more years this lifetime.

27:13.600 --> 27:14.760
Repay me in the next life.

27:20.000 --> 27:21.520
In the next one,

27:23.680 --> 27:25.280
you'll have to love me
for six years first.

27:26.560 --> 27:27.400
And then,

27:28.360 --> 27:29.480
I'll make sure

27:31.040 --> 27:32.360
you get what you wished for,

27:33.440 --> 27:34.960
just like I do now.

28:17.880 --> 28:19.320
What does this password imply?

28:21.200 --> 28:22.600
Guess it.

28:24.520 --> 28:26.480
It's not your birthday, not mine either.

28:28.400 --> 28:30.240
It's the date we first met.

28:46.240 --> 28:48.080
This table…

28:49.280 --> 28:50.320
Yeah, and more.

28:51.920 --> 28:53.280
And the cabinets too,

28:57.200 --> 28:59.200
and the sofa… all the same!

29:00.320 --> 29:01.280
Look.

29:02.880 --> 29:04.440
Doesn't it feel like our old place?

29:08.480 --> 29:09.840
You really put in the effort.

29:10.880 --> 29:13.960
I was afraid you wouldn't feel at home,
so I kept it just like before.

29:18.080 --> 29:19.080
Then, which room am I sleeping in?

29:19.760 --> 29:21.880
Whichever one you want.

29:22.480 --> 29:24.480
The kitchen. The bathroom.

29:25.560 --> 29:28.320
I'm not picky.
Wherever you sleep, I'll be there too.

29:30.040 --> 29:32.760
Sounds like you just want to share a room.

29:34.720 --> 29:37.080
Wouldn't this count
as living together before marriage?

29:39.720 --> 29:41.880
Isn't that bound to happen anyway?

29:41.960 --> 29:44.240
Can't I just exercise
my rights a little earlier?

29:45.200 --> 29:46.600
Haven't you already?

29:53.480 --> 29:54.880
When did you finish all this?

29:57.240 --> 29:58.120
Two years ago.

29:58.720 --> 30:02.160
But to make it feel like our home,
I remodeled it again.

30:05.600 --> 30:07.960
You brought all our memories back with it.

30:08.040 --> 30:08.920
It's perfect.

30:31.160 --> 30:33.760
It really is a paradise
for overworked employees.

30:33.840 --> 30:35.360
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

30:37.240 --> 30:40.080
Could it be that waiter from earlier?

30:40.800 --> 30:42.120
No way.

30:42.200 --> 30:46.000
The owner here is basically
the star of this whole street.

31:07.400 --> 31:08.600
Wen Shuangjiang,

31:10.560 --> 31:12.360
I've finally waited long enough for you.

31:29.920 --> 31:32.000
Last night, we lost a bracelet here.

34:32.440 --> 34:33.560
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

34:33.639 --> 34:34.719
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
